SOVREIGN

A Novel Future-Looking SDR

The world’s first stable cryptocurrency to be backed by a decentralized basket of demonstrably collateralized store-of-value assets

What is SoVReign?

An agile, future-looking SDR comprised of a balanced portfolio of non-inflationary reserve assets.

Currencies

Currency asset tokens that are truly backed 1:1 by the underlying asset.

Commodities

Commodities are a powerful inflation hedge and should be a part of any portfolio of reserve assets.

Cryptos

Store-of-value cryptos such as Ethereum and Bitcoin will continue to be used as inflation hedges.

The global reserve asset system is broken

The world needs a new future-looking global reserve asset that serves as a ‘store-of-value’ and medium of exchange

Inflation on the horizon

Excessive central bank intervention will lead to escalating inflation for current reserve currencies.

SoV will reign supreme

In the future store-of-value assets will reign supreme in global trade, as global enterprise seeks to hedge against inflation.

DeFi's USD problem

The DeFi space is dominated by USD pegged stable coins. We believe a new stable asset backed by inherently non-inflationary assets can get DeFi off of the dollar.

We are building a New-Age SDR

SoVReign uses a dual token system. The SVR ‘store of value’ token and the Reign governance token

Become a liquidity provider and receive the SVR store of value coin backed 1:1 by demonstrably collateralized asset tokens.

The REIGN token will be used by the community to vote on basket composition and other governance and protocol decisions.

Stable. Decentralised. Inflation resistent.

We believe only the community, together, can curate an agile, future-looking basket of assets fit for global trade

Tokenomics

We believe that the community should be in control that is why 71% of tokens will be issued to community participants as part of various incentive programmes
